title: Train Journey from the Drivers Eye View - Australia - 4 vids
description:
Train Journey - Driver-Engineer-eye-view - Australia - Karratha to Tom Price - 4 videos

I recorded this off TV in Germany. All 4 videos are in this torrent.

m4v format 

750 x 570 format

each video @ 1:10:00 min.
------------------

Just 5 hours of a freight train slowing moving through the Australian Outback. 

Not HD! This was recorded in the cab by a video recorder, through the window of the cab, so if you're used to HD, you won't find it here. There are dead bugs and crap on the windows, for example. However, the quality is pretty good, imo.

No music, just the sound of the train and engineer/radio, etc.

Screenshots: http://imgur.com/a/CWK5Y

Check my account for other train videos like this, many more to come
